WEBVTT

00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:31.256
Amir Khusro rightly said:

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:37.816
“Says Khusro, the river of love
runs in strange directions.

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:41.440
One who jumps into it drowns.
And one who drowns, gets across.”

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:44.440
(Applause)

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:46.376
No, no, it’s not that easy my friend.

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:50.016
It shocks the wits out of you,
your eyes turn pale …

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:54.140
This love is not easy,
just understand this much:

00:05:54.140 --> 00:05:57.940
it is a river of fire,
and you must go drowning

00:05:57.940 --> 00:05:59.090
(Applause)

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:01.949
Now the priest’s spell failed.